## Usage

1. **Set up family**: Name your family and customize colors
2. **Add members**: Create profiles for each family member
3. **Add items**: Click the "+" button to add items to wishlists
4. **Track purchases**: Mark items as purchased when bought
5. **Share**: Use the share button to send wishlists
6. **Chat**: Communicate with family in the chat
7. **Analyze**: View spending analytics in the dashboard

